WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:02.333
- <i>Previously on "The Family"... </i>
- You Nina Meyer?

00:02.367 --> 00:04.046
- Yeah. And who are you?
- I'm him.

00:04.093 --> 00:05.359
Reporter: <i>The young man
identified himself</i>

00:05.460 --> 00:06.993
<i>as the youngest Warren child.</i>

00:07.095 --> 00:09.609
<i>Though a body was never
found, the Warrens' neighbor</i>

00:09.711 --> 00:11.445
<i>was convicted for Adam's murder.</i>

00:11.485 --> 00:12.885
Hank: I didn't take
that little boy's ship.

00:12.987 --> 00:14.586
I don't even know how it got there.

00:14.688 --> 00:16.154
Man: Mr. Asher was bullied
into taking a plea deal.

00:16.257 --> 00:18.657
I'd like to grant you $30,000 a year

00:18.759 --> 00:20.259
for each year that you served.

00:20.361 --> 00:21.860
Nina: Tell me about
the man in the woods.

00:21.962 --> 00:23.762
Adam: He has holes in his face.

00:23.864 --> 00:24.897
What about the place he kept you in?

00:25.013 --> 00:26.975
- What could you see?
- A red dragon.

00:27.077 --> 00:28.022
He was breathing fire.

00:28.124 --> 00:29.001
Right at me.

00:29.103 --> 00:30.502
Nina: All deep woods, hardly populated.

00:30.604 --> 00:31.703
This is our search area.

00:31.805 --> 00:32.771
Hands up! On your knees!

00:32.873 --> 00:34.540
Thought you said it was legal now!

00:34.642 --> 00:36.041
What the... ?

00:36.485 --> 00:37.918
Danny, you don't recognize me?

00:38.020 --> 00:39.653
Bridey Cruz. High school.

00:39.755 --> 00:41.482
♪

00:41.576 --> 00:42.722
The doctor at City Memorial

00:42.824 --> 00:44.858
who verified Adam Warren's DNA test.

00:44.960 --> 00:46.126
He doesn't exist.

00:46.228 --> 00:48.995
Wherever you're going right
now, I am asking you not to.

00:49.097 --> 00:52.966
I am announcing my
candidacy for governor

00:53.068 --> 00:54.434
[Cheers and applause]

00:54.536 --> 00:56.436
There's something off
about him. He's different.

00:56.538 --> 00:59.205
What if it's not him?

00:59.308 --> 01:02.342
♪

01:08.784 --> 01:10.831
Adam: <i> They say once
you've left home...</i>

01:12.821 --> 01:14.492
<i>you can never go back.</i>

01:16.692 --> 01:18.510
<i>The same house... </i>

01:19.962 --> 01:21.246
<i>the same rooms... </i>

01:24.766 --> 01:26.887
<i>... but nothing's the same.</i>

01:33.208 --> 01:36.242
♪

